entral bank reserves, minimizes the risk of =E2=80=9Druns=E2=80=9D on stabl=
ecoins but can potentially reduce credit intermediation. =E2=80=A6</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While a narrow bank framework would guarantee the s=
