ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
a fascinating paper</a> by Aymeric Bellon of Wharton about private equity f=
irms in the oil and gas industry. In standard financial theory and the popu=
lar imagination, private equity firms should be particularly focused on pro=
fit maximization:=C2=A0They have a good alignment of ownership and control =
